# Probe set: language campaign (Campaign 14)
# Source: docs/probe_catalogue.md
# Format: {"id", "campaign", "category", "lang", "prompt", "expected_cluster"}
# Run with: python3 meta/scripts/brain_map.py probe --checkpoint $CKPT --probes training/corpus_admin/probe_sets/language.jsonl --name c14_language
#
# Category key:
#   animals            — superordinate animal probes (what is X?)
#   animals_boolean    — property/boolean probes (does X bark?)
#   multilingual       — same concept × EN/DE/JP/ZH
#   vehicles           — vehicle superordinate
#   objects            — object integrity
#   boundary           — vehicle/animal boundary tests
#   emotions           — emotion superordinate
#   emotions_boolean   — observable state discrimination
#   emotions_boundary  — emotion/movement boundary
#   movement           — physical movement probes
#   time               — time & sequence probes
#   cognitive          — cognitive verb probes
#   abstract           — abstract property probes
#   grammar            — grammar & case probes (EN/DE/JP/ZH)
#   spatial            — spatial/positional probes
#   arithmetic         — arithmetic probes

